Will build a 14.07 openwrt image for ar71xxx  

```bash
git clone git@github.com:botto/docker-openwrt-imagebuilder.git
cd docker-openwrt-imagebuilder
docker build -t imgb .
docker run imgb make info
docker run imgb make image PROFILE="TLWR703"
```

If you want to have the bin files dumped to a location you can find them then

```bash
cd docker-openwrt-imagebuilder
mkdir openwrt-bin
docker run -v openwrt-bin:/openwrt-bin imgb make image PROFILE="TLWR703" BIN_DIR="/openwrt-bin"
cd openwrt-bin
```


